Raiden is a member of the Japanese Pantheon and god of thunder.  He is also the patron of fletchers.  Raiden is often in the company of Susanoo the storm god.
Raiden's Realm is the Palace of Thunder in Othrys, on Carceri. His realm is a place of exploding light and thunder, insulated from the rest of the Plane by a thick covering of dark clouds. 

